**PLEASE READ ALL BEFORE SUBMITTING AN EMAIL**

Hey everyone! I have some exciting news. I will be guesting in Montréal at Studio Lapin Lapin from October 4-7! This will be my first time guesting anywhere and I am super excited :). Was also fun getting to animate this lil thing I haven’t done so since I was still in school lol.

The following flash is exclusively for my Montréal guest spot but any left over will of course be available to those in Toronto when I come back!

TO BOOK FOR MONTREAL:

I am accepting both flash and custom designs! Swipe to the end for the flash numbers and minimum sizes. Besides the flash shown here, I also have a few in my flash highlights. Flash is NON-REPEATABLE but I am always down to create a custom design based on existing flash if desired!

Please send an email to shlorp.tats@gmail.com with MONTRÉAL as the Subject Line including the following info (if information is incomplete I may not favour your submission):

➰Name
➰Pronouns
➰Flash number / Custom idea
➰Size
➰Placement
➰Preferred date (I cannot guarantee the exact date but I will always try to accommodate the best I can)

🖤 Thank you for your time! Looking forward to meeting you all 🖤

Just kidding! This is my last post of 2023. This year has been so amazing and I am so lucky to get to share my art with all of you like this.

It has been about a year and 7 months since I started my career as a tattoo artist and I have learned so much and met so many amazing people. I really could not imagine I would be where I am right now and I know little me would be absolutely freaking out to know that I get to draw my silly little things as a job (and people kinda  like them??)

I am so excited to see what happens in 2024!!! Thank you thank you from the bottom of my heart.
